These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: mango, corn, tomato, nectarine, papaya, pomegranate, cucumber
There are 7 different nationalities: polish, pakistani, turkish, indonesian, nigerian, canadian, argentine
 1. the person eating tomato is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating nectarine is not the canadian##6
 3. the polish is on the left of the person eating corn##1
 4. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
 5. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
 6. the polish is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 7. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere between the person eating corn and the pakistani##7
 8. the pakistani is on the left of the argentine##1
 9. the indonesian is somewhere between the person eating papaya and the turkish##7
10. the turkish is on the left or right of the polish##3
11. the nigerian is on the far left##1
12. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
13. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the right of the person eating pomegranate##5
14. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the person eating papaya##5
15. the person eating papaya is the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | tomato    | mango    | corn | pomegranate | nectarine | papaya    | cucumber |
| Nationality   | nigerian | polish | turkish  | canadian   | indonesian    | pakistani | argentine |

