.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: blueberry, lemon, orange, mango, grapes, apple, asparagus
The people have 7 different hobbies: magic-tricks, card-games, cooking, reading, video-games, photography, traveling
 1. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere between the person eating asparagus and the person eating lemon##7
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person eating mango##1
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 5. the person eating blueberry is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is card-games##7
 6. the person eating apple is somewhere between the person eating mango and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 7. the person eating grapes is somewhere between the person eating mango and the person eating lemon##7
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 9. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapes##5
10. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
11. the person who's hobby is photography is not the person eating asparagus##6
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
13. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person eating mango##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | asparagus  | orange | apple | mango | blueberry     | grapes | lemon  |
| Hobby   | cooking | photography | card-games  | traveling  | video-games | reading      | magic-tricks |

